name: Covalent Reality
description:
I honestly don't really know much about checkpoints, but while playing around to find a personal merge, I came up with this mix. It's a mix of Neverending Dream, Isopropanol Addiction Mix, and CarDos Animated. While the outputs aren't the exact style I was going for, I thought they looked nice and decided to share the mix with others.

I do know you must have "(greyscale, monochrome:1.0)," in your negative prompt for this to work well. If anyone can teach me how to fix that, I'd be happy to try.

Almost forgot! It does have VAE baked in.
